Special Fireteam. Bruant counts a a Métro for Fireteam composition.

NOTE: Troops possessing Inferior Infiltration cannot compose Fireteams in this Sectorial Army.

Note: The AVA of all 112 units is shared, so there can be a maximum of three 112s (any unit) in the Army List.

Example: Three 112s (Motorized); or two 112s (Motorized) one 112; or one 112 (Motorized) two 112s; or three 112s.

The 112 (Motorized) cannot be part of a Fireteam.
